  "synopsis": "On her own, out in the wide galaxy, while her friends struggle to escape the Empire and evade bounty hunters, Princess Leia steers her X-wing toward the heart of all her grief—a place she longs for, but should probably never revisit: the shattered ruins of her homeworld of Alderaan. * The homecoming you’ve waited 36 years to see! * Legendary Star Wars cover artist Hugh Fleming returns! * Brian Wood (The Massive, Conan) continues the best selling original trilogy tale!",
